CERTAIN TYPES OF HPV,

PROQUAD,

THE COMBINATION VACCINE

FOR SIMULTANEOUS VACCINATION AGAINST MEASLES, MUMPS, RUBELLA AND

VARICELLA, AND

ROTATEQ

TO HELP PROTECT AGAINST ROTAVIRUS

GASTROENTERITIS IN INFANTS AND CHILDREN. ALSO CONTRIBUTING TO

