NEUROMED RECEIVED AN UPFRONT PAYMENT OF $25 MILLION WHICH

THE COMPANY RECORDED AS RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT EXPENSE IN

2006. THE

83

SUCCESSFUL DEVELOPMENT AND LAUNCH OF NMED-160 FOR AN INITIAL

