ASKING FOR ADDITIONAL INFORMATION REGARDING THE COMPANYS

MARKETING AND SELLING ACTIVITIES RELATED TO TEXAS, INCLUDING

WITH RESPECT TO CERTAIN OF ITS NOMINAL PRICING PROGRAMS AND

